data.title: Royston Langdon
data.meta_description: Royston William Langdon is an English musician who is the lead singer and bassist of the English-American glam rock band Spacehog.
data.text:
Royston William Langdon (born 1 May 1972)[1] is an English musician who is the lead singer and bassist of the English-American glam rock band Spacehog.
